{"type":null,"faqId":19750,"title":"荣耀畅玩4X开启驾驶模式进行导航时，播放音乐和导航语音播报都是从手机里出声，而不是从蓝牙耳机里出声？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>您好，驾驶模式支持蓝牙耳机控制启动录音监听。这样的话，蓝牙耳机其他功能就不支持，比如声音输出等。因此使用驾驶模式的时候不能使用蓝牙听歌和听取导航的声音，这些声音只能从话筒中发出，关闭了驾驶模式一切正常。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":142,"faqType":"位置服务与导航","useful":0,"unUseful":3,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2970","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Location-Navigation","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1423274192000,"seriesProductName":"Cherry-CL10,Cherry-CL20","visitedTimes":742,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":6,"times":2,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"荣耀畅玩4X,驾驶模式,导航,导航语音播报","avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}